  "1757350": {
    "name": "ILL",
    "steam_appid": 1757350,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1757350/extras/f6bb8b394ad0808c49517bf6a9b768a9.poster.avif?t=1767716061\" width=616 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1757350/extras/f6bb8b394ad0808c49517bf6a9b768a9.webm?t=1767716061\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1757350/extras/f6bb8b394ad0808c49517bf6a9b768a9.mp4?t=1767716061\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>《ILL》是一款极致逼真的第一人称生存恐怖游戏，即便是该类型的老玩家也将面临前所未有的挑战。这款游戏将带你坠入阴森诡谲的暗黑世界，充满压迫感的剧情设计让游戏的每一分钟都令人窒息。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >开发团队堪称恐怖美学专家，曾与多位知名导演合作，参与过《长脚怪》、《直到黎明》、《致命录像带：超越》、《小丑回魂：欢迎来到德里镇》、《死亡天使》等影视作品的制作。如今，这群造梦者终于要实现夙愿——打造一款能撕裂理智、将你内心最深层的恐惧层层剥开的惊悚杰作。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1757350/extras/7cdba6edbb14425c2ae3f3fc30afa02e.webp?t=1767716061\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1757350/extras_big/7cdba6edbb14425c2ae3f3fc30afa02e.webp?t=1767716061 width=800 height=26 /></span>你将深陷一座巨型科研要塞的诡谲阴谋之中，面对神秘邪恶本源及其催生的可怖“异变体”。主角必须冲破重重阻碍，才能拯救心中至珍至重之物。《ILL》将让你身临其境，体验分秒必争的生存之战。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1757350/extras/f1b68953e8058e73f3cc399541961c42.poster.avif?t=1767716061\" width=616 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1757350/extras/f1b68953e8058e73f3cc399541961c42.webm?t=1767716061\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1757350/extras/f1b68953e8058e73f3cc399541961c42.mp4?t=1767716061\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1757350/extras/ed960307657719df922d43135e8cb627.webp?t=1767716061\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1757350/extras_big/ed960307657719df922d43135e8cb627.webp?t=1767716061 width=800 height=26 /></span>《ILL》以血腥的真实感突破类型极限：你可以无情肢解那些骇人怪物——撕裂的皮肉、裸露的骨骼、破碎的残躯将震撼你的灵魂，在你的记忆深处打下永恒的烙印。双声道音频系统强化沉浸感，每声惨叫都让你清晰感知痛苦。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1757350/extras/20fbe8a1a892848748f4a699bd0b9f70.poster.avif?t=1767716061\" width=616 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1757350/extras/20fbe8a1a892848748f4a699bd0b9f70.webm?t=1767716061\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1757350/extras/20fbe8a1a892848748f4a699bd0b9f70.mp4?t=1767716061\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1757350/extras/36750c6b15834b4282d2a05f47a8879c.webp?t=1767716061\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1757350/extras_big/36750c6b15834b4282d2a05f47a8879c.webp?t=1767716061 width=800 height=26 /></span>游戏中的敌人行为难以预测，而真实的物理效果让游戏世界不仅仅是静态背景，更成为玩法的重要组成部分——包括解谜环节。你的每个动作都可能影响怪物行为：它们会根据环境产生本能反应，并展现出令人毛骨悚然的智能。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1757350/extras/bc2840b5f1ed97f4d75506fcf9da798a.poster.avif?t=1767716061\" width=616 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1757350/extras/bc2840b5f1ed97f4d75506fcf9da798a.webm?t=1767716061\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1757350/extras/bc2840b5f1ed97f4d75506fcf9da798a.mp4?t=1767716061\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1757350/extras/08f7b4a76b354fe638f88fe59607ff4d.webp?t=1767716061\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1757350/extras_big/08f7b4a76b354fe638f88fe59607ff4d.webp?t=1767716061 width=800 height=26 /></span>每件武器都通过精细动画展现其独特的物理特性，让你真实感受手中武器的分量。精准射击远远不够——你需仔细检查军火库中每件武器的状态，并进行改装升级。完善的物品管理策略将决定生死存亡，而亲手制作的关键道具甚至可能扭转战局。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1757350/extras/60439555941eb8ee936282b8da7b424c.poster.avif?t=1767716061\" width=616 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1757350/extras/60439555941eb8ee936282b8da7b424c.webm?t=1767716061\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1757350/extras/60439555941eb8ee936282b8da7b424c.mp4?t=1767716061\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
